title: United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Ores Slag & Ash
description: Imports of Intra EU - Ores, Slag & Ash in the United Kingdom increased to 62.45 GBP Million in September from 40.42 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Intra EU - Ores, Slag & Ash in the United Kingdom averaged 25.85 GBP Million from 1996 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 128.44 GBP Million in February of 2022 and a record low of 2.72 GBP Million in August of 1999. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Intra EU - Ores, Slag & Ash.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
